5 balances as follows:
6 (a) The estimated annual revenue shall not be greater than one
7 hundred seven percent of program cash fund appropriations allocated for
8 the Plant Protection and Plant Pest Act; and
9 (b) The estimated fiscal year-end cash fund balance shall not be
10 greater than seventeen percent of program cash fund appropriations
11 allocated for the act.
